// https://developer.apple.com/ios/human-interface-guidelines/visual-design/color/

const colors = {
    red: '#FF3B30',
    orange: '#FF9500',
    yellow: '#FFCC00',
    green: '#4CD964',
    tealBlue: '#5AC8FA',
    blue: '#007AFF',
    purple: '#5856D6',
    pink: '#FF2D55',
  
    white: '#FFFFFF',
    customGray: '#EFEFF4',
    lightGray: '#E5E5EA',
    lightGray2: '#D1D1D6',
    midGray: '#C7C7CC',
    gray: '#8E8E93',
    black: '#000000',
  }
  
  export default colors
